news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)</li>\n<li>CoWoS 暨設備萬潤 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6187:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6187\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6187-TW</a>)、辛耘 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3563:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3563\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3563-TW</a>)、致茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2360:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2360\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2360-TW</a>)、德律 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3030:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3030\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3030-TW</a>)、華景電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6788:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6788\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6788-TW</a>)、漢唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2404:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2404\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2404-TW</a>)</li>\n<li> 石英元件加高 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8182:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8182\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8182-TW</a>)、泰藝 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8289-TW</a>)、MCU 新唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4919-TW</a>)</li>\n<li> 二極體強茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2481-TW</a>)、台半 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5425-TW</a>)、被動信昌電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6173:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6173\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6173-TW</a>)、鈺凱 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:5228:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5228\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5228-TW</a>)</li>\n<li> 特化永光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1711-TW</a>)、雙鍵 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)、三晃 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1721:STOCK:COMMON\" data-